<msItem xml:id="ms_i1.1">
<locus from="1r" to="6v" facs="003"/>
<title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT6799RHintro">Homily by Rǝtuʿa Hāymānot on the Incarnation</title>
<incipit xml:lang="gez">ድርሳን፡ ዘደረሰ፡ አባ፡ ሰላማ፡ በእንተ፡ ሥላሴ፡ ወሥጋዌሁ፡ ለወልደ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ ሕያው፡ ወሕማማቲሁ፡ ወዕርገቱ፡ ውስተ፡ ሰማያት፡</incipit>
<note>The attribution of the introductory homily to ʾabbā <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS8387SalamaI">Salāmā</persName> is unique among the Rǝtuʿa Hāymānot manuscripts.</note>
<textLang mainLang="gez"/>
</msItem>

